readme:
# Lodash.js Snippets for Atom
Some snippets to quickly use lodash library in Atom.

# Note:
This is a fork of project `lodash-snippets` by @richtmat, which in turn was inspired by `atom-undescorejs` (@tianp). I forked the project because of the styling difference between @richtmat and me.
I don't like spaces between my parentheses but apparently he likes it, moreover the parentheses weren't even consistent, which drived me nuts so.

## Install
```bash
apm install lodash-snippets
```
Or
```
Settings ➔ Install ➔ Search for `lodash`
```
